text: Pichugi () is a rural locality (a village) in Toykinskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 6 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 10 km south-west from Toykino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Pichugi
